page.title: 10Fraserburgh Limited
page.content: Fraserburgh Limited is trying to create more jobs for people in Fraserbugh .In Fraserbugh unemployment is very high and they are trying to cut it down.They have already helped lots of people to get a job.If you want to make a company you need lots of money and a very good idea.If you have a good idea and lots of money but not enough, they will give you some money and then they will take you to the bank and they will give you the rest. Fraserbugh Limited is planned to last for three years.If it is very successful it won't need to to go on.If it is moderately successful it will go on for another three years and if it is a failure it will be called off.It has also helped eleven companies and it helped one man to make a company.
